<tmc-service-inc>
<pub id="RM0251U">
<servcat id="39">
<name>RESTRAINTS</name>
<section id="1000Y_S0016" variety="S0016">
<name>SUPPLEMENTAL RESTRAINT SYSTEM</name>
<ttl id="1000Y_S0016_72ZS3_T00CJ" variety="T00CJ">
<name>AIRBAG SYSTEM</name>
<para id="RM000002C9O000X" category="C" type-id="8020H" name-id="RS2D5-01" from="200601">
<dtccode>B1610/13</dtccode>
<dtcname>Front Airbag Sensor RH Malfunction</dtcname>
<subpara id="RM000002C9O000X_01" type-id="60" category="03" proc-id="RM0250U___0000BZX00000">
<name>DESCRIPTION</name>
<content5 releasenbr="1">
<ptxt>The front airbag sensor RH consists of the diagnostic circuit, the frontal deceleration sensor, etc.</ptxt>
<ptxt>If the center airbag sensor assembly receives signals from the frontal deceleration sensor, it determines whether the SRS should be activated.</ptxt>
<ptxt>DTC B1610/13 is recorded when a malfunction is detected in the front airbag sensor RH.</ptxt>
<table frame="all" pgwide="1">
<tgroup cols="3">
<colspec colname="col1" colwidth="1.42in"/>
<colspec colname="col2" colwidth="2.83in"/>
<colspec colname="col3" colwidth="2.83in"/>
<thead>
<row>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>DTC No.</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>DTC Detection Condition</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>Trouble Area</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>B1610/13</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<list1 type="unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>Front airbag sensor RH malfunction</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>Center airbag sensor assembly malfunction</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<list1 type="unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>Front airbag sensor RH</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>Center airbag sensor assembly</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</content5>
</subpara>
<subpara id="RM000002C9O000X_02" type-id="32" category="03" proc-id="RM0250U___0000BZY00000">
<name>WIRING DIAGRAM</name>
<content5 releasenbr="1">
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="H002750E34" width="7.106578999in" height="5.787629434in"/>
</figure>
</content5>
</subpara>
<subpara id="RM000002C9O000X_03" type-id="51" category="05">
<name>INSPECTION PROCEDURE</name>
</subpara>
<subpara id="RM000002C9O000X_04" type-id="01" category="01">
<name>PROCEDURE</name>
<testgrp id="RM000002C9O000X_04_0001" proc-id="RM0250U___0000BZZ00000">
<testtitle>CHECK FRONT AIRBAG SENSOR RH</testtitle>
<content6 releasenbr="1">
<test1>
<ptxt>Turn the ignition switch off.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C114793E01" width="2.775699831in" height="3.779676365in"/>
</figure>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Disconnect the negative (-) terminal cable from the battery, and wait for at least 90 seconds.</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Interchange the front airbag sensor LH with RH and connect the connectors to them.</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Connect the negative (-) terminal cable to the battery, and wait for at least 2 seconds.</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Turn the ignition switch on (IG), and wait for at least 60 seconds.</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Clear the DTCs stored in the memory (See page <xref label="Seep01" href="RM000000XFE00YX"/>).</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Turn the ignition switch off.</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Turn the ignition switch on (IG), and wait for at least 60 seconds.</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Check the DTCs (See page <xref label="Seep02" href="RM000000XFE00YX"/>).</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>Result</title>
<table>
<tgroup cols="2">
<colspec colname="COL1" colwidth="2.89in"/>
<colspec colname="COL2" colwidth="1.24in"/>
<thead>
<row>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>Result</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>Proceed to</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>DTC B1610/13 is output.</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>A</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>DTC B1615/14 is output.</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>B</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>DTC B1610/13 and B1615/14 are not output.</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>C</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
<atten4>
<ptxt>Codes other than DTC B1610/13 and B1615/14 may be output at this time, but they are not related to this check.</ptxt>
</atten4>
</test1>
</content6>
<res>
<down ref="RM000002C9O000X_04_0004" fin="true">C</down>
<right ref="RM000002C9O000X_04_0002" fin="true">A</right>
<right ref="RM000002C9O000X_04_0003" fin="true">B</right>
</res>
</testgrp>
<testgrp id="RM000002C9O000X_04_0002">
<testtitle>REPLACE CENTER AIRBAG SENSOR ASSEMBLY<xref label="Seep01" href="RM000000UWV00HX"/>
</testtitle>
</testgrp>
<testgrp id="RM000002C9O000X_04_0003">
<testtitle>REPLACE FRONT AIRBAG SENSOR RH<xref label="Seep01" href="RM000000UWZ00KX"/>
</testtitle>
</testgrp>
<testgrp id="RM000002C9O000X_04_0004">
<testtitle>USE SIMULATION METHOD TO CHECK<xref label="Seep01" href="RM000000XFD00ZX"/>
</testtitle>
</testgrp>
</subpara>
</para>
</ttl>
</section>
